title: 114: The Fan Food Finds Episode
itunes:title: The Fan Food Finds Episode
description: In this episode, Lisa and the gang are trying food finds from you, the listeners! Finds like cookie-flavored powdered peanut butter, meat bars, reduced-sodium ramen, powdered monkfruit sweetener, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, the find of all finds, a low-calorie snack made from peas that tastes better than Funyuns!!! It got the highest score ever on Lisa’s scale! So push play now, and then head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of all the finds mentioned in the episode.
itunes:summary: We asked you what your favorite food finds are, and then we tried them on this week’s episode of Chew the Right Thing!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
dc:creator: Lisa Lillien
